Title: R Package for Making ggplot2 Plots Accessible
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package that extracts data from ggplot2 plots to make them accessible via JavaScript backend, similar to py-maidr for matplotlib/seaborn. Focuses on functional architecture and modular design for easy extension to new plot types.
